com.wdullaer.materialdatetimepicker.time

Class Timepoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wdullaer.materialdatetimepicker.time.Timepoint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable, java.lang.Comparable<Timepoint>

    public class Timepoint
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable, java.lang.Comparable<Timepoint>
    Simple utility class that represents a time in the day up to second precision The time input is expected to use 24 hour mode. Fields are modulo'd into their correct ranges. It does not handle timezones. Created by wdullaer on 13/10/15.
